Notes:
had the source files for nearly 2 weeks, but was stuck with no audio for it,
at least i had time to prepare my video. quality was good, dark scenes were ok but improveable.
 
finally exclusive video+line went up, but 1min was missing in the middle of the movie, which i had now no audio.
also video looked like a reencode of a reencode even had a watermark in it.
 
mine is clean and a lot better quality and has the missing minute inside.
thankfully cadance came up with the missing audio so i can do a full movie now.
 
 
Encode:
quality on video was already very nice, daylight scenes were bright enough but darker scenes needed more,
so i split the video in pieces and made all dark scenes brighter, very watchable now.
 
Line Audio was nice, lipsynced to my video.
 
got very nice and will do me till retail
enjoy
